Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:06.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,It is the turbulent Sengoku period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:11.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,Warlords keep on fighting day and night over\NJipangu State, where Karakuri people live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:16.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,Karakuri martial artists were sharpening their swords, dreaming of victory and honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:23.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,And now, a wild hero has arrived, seeking to be the number one Karakuri martial artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:26.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi is here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:33.22,TitleOP,en,0,0,40,,{\an8\fs32\fade(770,0)}Karakuri Kengouden
